<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - PerSeptive Biosystems.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - PerSeptive Biosystems.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Deutshe Morgan Grenfell said it initiated coverage of PerSeptive Biosystems Inc as buy.</p>
<p>-- Set a 12-18 month price target of $14 a share.</p>
<p>-- Expects earnings to turn positive in the fourth quarter of fiscal 1997.</p>
<p>-- Believes company is on a journey back to health.</p>
<p>-- Said company's new, more directed vision includes continued momentum in its base purification and analysis segment.</p>
<p>-- PerSeptive gained 5/8 to 8-3/4.</p>
</text>
